Name: changePubKey.newPkHash
Description: Public key hash to be set for an account

Name: changePubKey.fee
Description: Fee to pay for operation, paid in token

Name: changePubKey.validFrom
Description: Unix timestamp from which the block with this transaction can be processed

Name: changePubKey.validUntil
Description: Unix timestamp until which the block with this transaction can be processed

Name: changePubKey.ethAuthData (optional)
Description: Data which is used to verify the Ethereum signature

Name: returns
Description: Signed zkSync change public key transaction
